---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import TrustCredentials from "../components/TrustCredentials.astro";
import InlineQuoteForm from "../components/InlineQuoteForm.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="Rittenworx: Licensed, insured private maintenance and handyman service in Madison & Huntsville AL. 15+ years experience. Quality workmanship guaranteed."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Rittenworx</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your trusted partner for private maintenance, repairs, and improvements
        in North Alabama.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">My Story</h2>
        <p
          class="text-gray-800 font-medium mb-6 text-xl italic border-l-4 border-orange-500 pl-4"
        >
          "Jack of all trades and a master of none, Your satisfaction is
          guaranteed with a job well done."
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          I grew up in Maryland working on yachts—which are essentially floating
          homes—where I first learned the value of meticulous craftsmanship. I
          later pursued business construction in school, learning everything
          from masonry and block-laying to framing, blueprint drawing, and
          professional window and door installation. Since then, I’ve spent over
          15 years honing my skills as a carpenter by trade and an all-around
          problem solver.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          My grandfather and uncle always told me that being a "Jack of all
          trades" is better than being a master of one, because the more useful
          you are in the world, the more successful you may become. Rather than
          specializing in one narrow field, I operate as a private maintenance
          professional for residential and commercial properties. In my 7+ years
          of running this owner-operator, family-owned business, I’ve found that
          my work boils down to four main things: <strong
            >Repairs, Replacements, Installations, and Assemblies</strong
          >. If you need it done, I can perform one of those functions to get it
          done right (though I do opt to skip carpet and tile!).
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          I am a fully licensed business and carry a $1 million liability
          insurance policy for your complete peace of mind. I also bring a
          strict standard of quality to every project: I will not accept a job
          unless I know I can do it correctly. Any repair I make is guaranteed
          to serve its purpose, and in the rare event of a failure, I stand by
          my work with a rapid response and immediate repair.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          My goal has never been to get rich; I just want to make an honest
          living getting the most out of my skills, and providing reliable,
          high-quality work to my community. I promise to respond to written
          requests within 24 hours and to voicemails within 3 hours. I treat
          every home with respect and guarantee your satisfaction.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">
        Our Values
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-900"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Integrity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Honest assessments and fair pricing. We'll never recommend work you
            don't need.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-900"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Efficiency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            We respect your time and complete projects efficiently without
            cutting corners.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-900"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Care</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            We treat your home like our own, keeping workspaces clean and
            respecting your property.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-900"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Quality</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Every repair and installation meets our high standards. Satisfaction
            guaranteed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Credentials Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">
        Why Trust Us
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">10+</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Years of Experience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">500+</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Projects Completed</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">100%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Satisfaction Guarantee</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">
              Fully Licensed & Insured
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700">
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                General liability insurance
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700">
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Workers' compensation coverage
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700">
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Background checked
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Our Guarantee</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We stand behind our work. If you're not completely satisfied with
              any repair or installation, we'll make it right at no additional
              cost. Your satisfaction is our top priority.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <InlineQuoteForm />

  <TrustCredentials />

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-orange-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8">
        Let us show you why your neighbors trust Rittenworx.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-orange-500 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg inline-block"
      >
        Get Your Free Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
